At least I see the outcome of the required training and courses for trainers, table officials and arbitrators.
I'm proud of that.
What are you doing today?
I like listening to music, watching videos of music of my time in YouTube, enjoying my grandchildren and occasionally going to a basketball game.
And of course I enjoy the company of my wife Isabel, who was always at my side.
